---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Veterans Program"
  description="Weyland-Yutani is the chief employer of Asian Conflict veterans. Our dedicated transition programs, skills mapping, and veteran benefits make W-Y the top choice for military professionals."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="bg-black pt-36">
    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="relative min-h-[60vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden border-b-4 border-[#FFC600]">
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-20"></div>
      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute top-0 left-0 right-0"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 text-center py-24">
        <div class="inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-[#FFC600] text-black font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-8 clip-corner">
          CAREERS &mdash; VETERANS
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-black text-white mb-8 leading-none uppercase">
          VETERANS <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">PROGRAM</span>
        </h1>

        <div class="h-1 w-64 bg-[#FFC600] mx-auto mb-8"></div>

        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto uppercase tracking-wide font-mono">
          YOUR SERVICE PREPARED YOU TO LEAD. WE ARE PREPARED TO SUPPORT YOUR NEXT MISSION.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- COMMITMENT -->
    <section class="relative py-24 bg-[#0a0a0a] border-b-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="industrial-grid-dense absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest font-mono">OUR COMMITMENT</span>
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-black text-white mt-4 mb-6 uppercase">
              HONORING <span class="text-[#FFC600]">SERVICE</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed mb-6">
              WEYLAND-YUTANI IS THE CHIEF EMPLOYER OF ASIAN CONFLICT VETERANS, WITH 35% OF ALL TRANSITIONING SERVICE MEMBERS JOINING OUR RANKS IN 2038. THIS IS NOT A STATISTIC WE TAKE FOR GRANTED. IT IS A RESPONSIBILITY WE HONOR EVERY DAY.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed mb-6">
              MILITARY PROFESSIONALS BRING DISCIPLINE, LEADERSHIP, AND OPERATIONAL EXCELLENCE THAT NO CIVILIAN TRAINING CAN REPLICATE. OUR VETERAN PROGRAMS ARE DESIGNED TO TRANSLATE THOSE STRENGTHS INTO FULFILLING CORPORATE CAREERS.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed">
              FROM THE COLONIAL MARINES TO OUR SECURITY DIVISION, FROM FLEET OPERATIONS TO CORPORATE LEADERSHIP, VETERANS FIND THEIR SKILLS VALUED AND THEIR EXPERIENCE RESPECTED AT EVERY LEVEL OF OUR ORGANIZATION.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="corp-card p-6 text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl font-black text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow mb-2">35%</div>
              <div class="text-white font-bold text-sm uppercase">ASIAN CONFLICT VETERANS HIRED</div>
              <div class="text-gray-600 font-mono text-xs uppercase">2038 TRANSITION COHORT</div>
            </div>
            <div class="corp-card p-6 text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl font-black text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow mb-2">TOP 50</div>
              <div class="text-white font-bold text-sm uppercase">NAFE COMPANIES FOR EXECUTIVE WOMEN</div>
              <div class="text-gray-600 font-mono text-xs uppercase">2055 RECOGNITION</div>
            </div>
            <div class="corp-card p-6 text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl font-black text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow mb-2">50K+</div>
              <div class="text-white font-bold text-sm uppercase">VETERAN EMPLOYEES</div>
              <div class="text-gray-600 font-mono text-xs uppercase">ACROSS ALL DIVISIONS</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- TRANSITION PROGRAMS -->
    <section class="relative py-24 bg-black border-b-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest font-mono">PROGRAMS</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mt-4 uppercase">
            TRANSITION <span class="text-[#FFC600]">PROGRAMS</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-sm uppercase tracking-wide mt-4 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            STRUCTURED PATHWAYS FROM MILITARY SERVICE TO CORPORATE CAREER EXCELLENCE
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <span class="text-black text-lg font-black">1</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase">SKILLS ASSESSMENT</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed">
              OUR PROPRIETARY MILITARY-TO-CORPORATE SKILLS MAPPING SYSTEM TRANSLATES YOUR MILITARY EXPERIENCE INTO CORPORATE COMPETENCIES. OVER 2,000 MILITARY OCCUPATIONAL SPECIALTIES MAPPED TO W-Y ROLES WITH 95% ACCURACY.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <span class="text-black text-lg font-black">2</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase">BRIDGE TRAINING</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed">
              8-12 WEEK PAID TRAINING PROGRAMS BRIDGE ANY KNOWLEDGE GAPS BETWEEN YOUR MILITARY SPECIALIZATION AND YOUR TARGET CORPORATE ROLE. CONDUCTED AT OUR DEDICATED VETERAN TRANSITION CENTERS ON EARTH AND LUNA.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <span class="text-black text-lg font-black">3</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase">MENTORED ONBOARDING</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed">
              EACH VETERAN HIRE IS PAIRED WITH A SENIOR MENTOR, OFTEN THEMSELVES A VETERAN, FOR THE FIRST YEAR OF EMPLOYMENT. THIS ENSURES A SMOOTH CULTURAL TRANSITION AND ACCELERATED INTEGRATION INTO CORPORATE OPERATIONS.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <span class="text-black text-lg font-black">4</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase">LEADERSHIP FAST TRACK</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed">
              VETERANS WITH COMMAND EXPERIENCE ARE ELIGIBLE FOR OUR ACCELERATED LEADERSHIP PROGRAM, PLACING QUALIFIED CANDIDATES INTO MANAGEMENT ROLES WITHIN 18 MONTHS. MILITARY LEADERSHIP EXPERIENCE IS DIRECTLY CREDITED.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <span class="text-black text-lg font-black">5</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase">COLONIAL MARINE PARTNERSHIP</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed">
              OUR FORMAL PARTNERSHIP WITH THE UNITED STATES COLONIAL MARINE CORPS TRANSITION ASSISTANCE PROGRAM PROVIDES SEAMLESS CAREER PATHWAYS FOR SEPARATING MARINES INTO SECURITY, OPERATIONS, AND LOGISTICS ROLES.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <span class="text-black text-lg font-black">6</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase">FAMILY SUPPORT</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed">
              COMPREHENSIVE RELOCATION ASSISTANCE, SPOUSAL EMPLOYMENT SUPPORT, AND DEPENDENT EDUCATION PROGRAMS ENSURE YOUR ENTIRE FAMILY IS SUPPORTED DURING THE TRANSITION FROM MILITARY TO CORPORATE LIFE.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SKILLS MAPPING -->
    <section class="relative py-24 bg-[#0a0a0a] border-b-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="industrial-grid-dense absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest font-mono">CAREER MAPPING</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mt-4 uppercase">
            MILITARY TO <span class="text-[#FFC600]">CORPORATE</span>
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="corp-card p-8 md:p-12">
          <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed mb-8 text-center">
            YOUR MILITARY EXPERIENCE TRANSLATES DIRECTLY TO HIGH-VALUE CORPORATE ROLES
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 items-center bg-black p-4 border border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner">
              <div class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase">COMBAT ARMS / INFANTRY</div>
              <div class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-xs text-center">&rarr;</div>
              <div class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase">SECURITY OPERATIONS, COLONY PROTECTION</div>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 items-center bg-black p-4 border border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner">
              <div class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase">ENGINEERING / CONSTRUCTION</div>
              <div class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-xs text-center">&rarr;</div>
              <div class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase">COLONY INFRASTRUCTURE, TERRAFORMING OPS</div>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 items-center bg-black p-4 border border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner">
              <div class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase">AVIATION / FLIGHT OPERATIONS</div>
              <div class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-xs text-center">&rarr;</div>
              <div class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase">FLEET OPERATIONS, NAVIGATION</div>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 items-center bg-black p-4 border border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner">
              <div class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase">LOGISTICS / SUPPLY CHAIN</div>
              <div class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-xs text-center">&rarr;</div>
              <div class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase">CORPORATE LOGISTICS, COLONY SUPPLY</div>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 items-center bg-black p-4 border border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner">
              <div class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase">MEDICAL / HEALTH SERVICES</div>
              <div class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-xs text-center">&rarr;</div>
              <div class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase">HEALTH SCIENCES, MEDPOD OPERATIONS</div>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 items-center bg-black p-4 border border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner">
              <div class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase">INTELLIGENCE / ANALYSIS</div>
              <div class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-xs text-center">&rarr;</div>
              <div class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase">CYBERSECURITY, CORPORATE INTELLIGENCE</div>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 items-center bg-black p-4 border border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner">
              <div class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase">COMMAND / SENIOR NCO</div>
              <div class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-xs text-center">&rarr;</div>
              <div class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase">CORPORATE MANAGEMENT, DIVISION LEADERSHIP</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- VETERAN ERG -->
    <section class="relative py-24 bg-black border-b-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest font-mono">COMMUNITY</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mt-4 uppercase">
            VETERAN EMPLOYEE <span class="text-[#FFC600]">RESOURCE GROUP</span>
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-4">W-Y VETERANS ALLIANCE</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed mb-4">
              OUR LARGEST EMPLOYEE RESOURCE GROUP WITH OVER 12,000 MEMBERS ACROSS ALL OPERATING LOCATIONS. THE W-Y VETERANS ALLIANCE PROVIDES PEER SUPPORT, PROFESSIONAL NETWORKING, AND COMMUNITY ENGAGEMENT FOR VETERAN EMPLOYEES AND THEIR FAMILIES.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase status-active">MONTHLY NETWORKING EVENTS</li>
              <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase status-active">ANNUAL VETERANS LEADERSHIP SUMMIT</li>
              <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase status-active">PEER MENTORSHIP CIRCLES</li>
              <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase status-active">COMMUNITY SERVICE INITIATIVES</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-4">VETERAN-SPECIFIC BENEFITS</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed mb-4">
              IN ADDITION TO OUR STANDARD BENEFITS PACKAGE, VETERAN EMPLOYEES RECEIVE ENHANCED SUPPORT RECOGNIZING THEIR UNIQUE SERVICE AND SACRIFICE.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase status-active">MILITARY SERVICE CREDIT TOWARD SENIORITY</li>
              <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase status-active">ENHANCED MENTAL HEALTH AND PTSD SUPPORT</li>
              <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase status-active">RESERVE DUTY LEAVE WITH FULL PAY</li>
              <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase status-active">VETERANS DAY PAID HOLIDAY</li>
              <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase status-active">SIGNING BONUS FOR QUALIFIED VETERANS</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="relative py-24 bg-[#0a0a0a]">
      <div class="industrial-grid-dense absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
        <div class="terminal">
          <div class="terminal-content text-center">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-white mb-6 uppercase">
              &gt; YOUR NEXT MISSION AWAITS
            </h2>
            <p class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-sm uppercase mb-8 leading-relaxed">
              WHETHER YOU ARE SEPARATING FROM ACTIVE DUTY OR SEEKING A NEW CHALLENGE AFTER YEARS IN THE PRIVATE SECTOR,
              WEYLAND-YUTANI IS READY TO PUT YOUR EXPERIENCE TO WORK.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
              <a href="/careers" class="btn-primary text-sm">VIEW OPEN POSITIONS</a>
              <a href="/contact" class="btn-secondary text-sm">CONTACT VETERAN RECRUITING</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .clip-corner {
    clip-path: polygon(8px 0, 100% 0, 100% calc(100% - 8px), calc(100% - 8px) 100%, 0 100%, 0 8px);
  }
</style>
